# LearnHub Configuration Guide

The LearnHub application uses standard Spring Boot configuration with YAML files.

## Application Configuration
- [application.yml](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/resources/application.yml) - Main application configuration
- [application-dev.yml](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/resources/application-dev.yml) - Development environment overrides

## Key Configuration Properties
- Database connection settings
- Redis cache configuration
- File storage configuration
- Security settings
- Cors configuration

## Build Configuration
- [pom.xml](mdc:learnhub-api/pom.xml) - Main project Maven POM file 
- [learnhub-api/pom.xml](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/pom.xml) - API module POM file
- [learnhub-common/pom.xml](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-common/pom.xml) - Common module POM file
- [learnhub-course/pom.xml](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-course/pom.xml) - Course module POM file
- [learnhub-resource/pom.xml](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-resource/pom.xml) - Resource module POM file
- [learnhub-system/pom.xml](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-system/pom.xml) - System module POM file

## Docker Configuration
- [Dockerfile](mdc:learnhub-api/Dockerfile) - Docker image definition
- [Dockerfile.local](mdc:learnhub-api/Dockerfile.local) - Local development Docker configuration
- [compose.yml](mdc:compose.yml) - Docker Compose service definitions
